###########################################################
This is a repository containing scripts to
* query the Config Database
* insert new records into the database
* insert partial records into the db
###########################################################

Requirements:
-- An installation of the PostgreSQL CDB API either through MAUS or stand-alone
---- https://bazaar.launchpad.net/~janusz-martyniak/mcdb/mice.cdb.client.api-python/files/head:/dist/

The structure is broken down by DB services implemented in the API:

1. beamline
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
2. coolingchannel
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
3. absorber
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
4. tracker
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
5. calib
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
6. batch iteration
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
7. mc-serial
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
8. runinfo
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table
9. utils
--> to query the beamline table by run or optics tags
--> to insert begin, beamline, end records into the beamline table



